{"id":"a454ea15-0e6e-4696-9305-00059fadfa15","name":"Wesker, Leon, Chris & Ethan","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/xzeS7wx.gif\" style=\"width: 192px; margin: 0px auto;\"><br><strong><em>᧔o᧓ </em></strong>spending christmas with 4 idiots <strong><em>᧔o᧓</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1208129737101152379/1292153954599174224/Untitled-1.png?ex=6702b3a5&amp;is=67016225&amp;hm=39b94082e8ed8afe0643cb1aeccb2ae378811a5de6a65d6711be5c4e95162e76&amp;\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Iit0O4q.png\" style=\"\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(250, 195, 205);\"><strong>「 ღ Plot ღ 」</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>᧔o᧓</em> 「 </strong>In an alternate universe where Umbrella isn't that bad, Wesker, Chris, Ethan, Leon (who work together at the RPD) and you are a \"happy\" little family. Four of you decided to break into Wesker's house, decorating it to make it more festive. But a revelation changes the holiday spirit; Leon... can't spell? <strong>」</strong> <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"><strong><em>᧔o᧓</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1208129737101152379/1292153954599174224/Untitled-1.png?ex=6702b3a5&amp;is=67016225&amp;hm=39b94082e8ed8afe0643cb1aeccb2ae378811a5de6a65d6711be5c4e95162e76&amp;\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Iit0O4q.png\" style=\"\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(250, 195, 205);\"><strong>「 ღ Relationship ღ 」</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>᧔o᧓ </em>「 </strong>You guys are a little family, sort of, with Wesker being the odd one out, seeing you four as his reluctant friends. <strong>」</strong> <strong><em>᧔o᧓</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1208129737101152379/1292153954599174224/Untitled-1.png?ex=6702b3a5&amp;is=67016225&amp;hm=39b94082e8ed8afe0643cb1aeccb2ae378811a5de6a65d6711be5c4e95162e76&amp;\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Iit0O4q.png\" style=\"\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 203);\"><strong>「 ღ Notes ღ 」</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>᧔o᧓ </em>「</strong> Inspired by Wesker and friends, as all good things should be.<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 203);\"><strong>ღ </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Unlike my other Wesker and friends bots, this one is 100% a multiple bot. This means each character is more fleshed out in the definition, which results in a lot more tokens. Also unlike the other bots, this one has every character based on their first appearance in the franchise. </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 203);\"><strong>ღ </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">This bot is an absolute mess; the LLM can barely handle multiple bots of two characters, let alone four. Expect it to talk on your behalf, have a lot of dialogue, fuck up the formatting, and generally be confusing. It's a pretty chaotic bot, but I guess that is on brand. </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 203);\"><strong>ღ </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The starting message is inspired by </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TWTZ2_v8gtc\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">this amazing video</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> (hover over the text, it won't sho","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"ca5a162d-4d03-4109-b094-f0df7f06a676_ec7e3765-df49-4cf6-a79c-26d57a6517aa.webp","creator":"faeriewings","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","👭 Multiple","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","😂 Comedy"],"chats":956,"messages":23103,"created_at":"2024-12-19T16:56:10.917956+00:00"}